messages: fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:22): why hello there kind fellow
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:22): how art thou on this fine day?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:22): That's very assuming. It's entirely possible I'm not kind, or a fellow.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:23): Ah very clever chap, I do indeed respect a man with a good sense about him
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:23): I'm a clever lady, as it were.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:24): Oh a female, I beg your pardon miss
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:24): I forgive you.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:25): Clever and kind a very good combination
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:25): So tell me my dear how art thou on such a fine day?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:26): I'm marvelous, though I'm not sure it's even possible to be both clever and kind m'dear.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:26): might I inquire as to your logic behind your previous statement?
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:28): also it is good to hear that fortune has smiled upon you and blessed you this day
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:28): Well, cleverness is rather wicked in nature don't you think?
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:29): I must agree, but on the other hand is it not possible to use this gift as a chance to give happiness unto others?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:29): I do not. Cleverness is art form inspired by cruelty.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:30): perhaps the term that should apply to you then is indeed intelligent as it were
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:31): While others may take delight in it's creative perversions, it's origin is in spite. It would not be the first time I have been accused of cleverness.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:32): I appologize, if i might be so bold could i perchance have the pleasure of knowing the name of this fair maiden?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:33): Jade, and you Sir are?
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:34): Oh how rude of me, I am Jairus, I hail from the state of idaho, the homestead of many of the worlds finest Potato farmers
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:35): That's some fine turn of the century english you have there Jairus.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:35): ah yes quite
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:36): so Jade, tell me of thy self.
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:37): I'm a simple girl, often too clever for my own good and almost perpetually heartbroken.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:38): I'm sorry to hear that, it is indeed a very sad day when one's heart breaks...
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:39): It seems I'm cursed with an overactive love muscle.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:40): And which muscle does thou speak of?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:40): The heart, naturally.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:42): such a fine young women, i don't mean to intrude or overstep my bounds, but by chance is it that no man will take your hand as a suitor?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:43): None of any merit.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:43): tis a sad day indeed, it appears that civalry is all but dead
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:44): It certainly is.
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:44): I'm afraid it is of a rather ungodly hour good Sir, and that I must take my leave.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:45): oh but before you depart is there possibly anyway of staying in contact with you, i truly have enjoyed our conversation, perhaps through messenger?
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:46): yes indeed the mail that is hot
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:47): thank you madame, i shall write to you shortly
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:47): until we meet again may fortune smile upon you :)
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:47): yes indeed
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:47): Add again.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:47): twas a silly name given to me by dear compatriots
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:48): Forgive me, but I am weary of those that call themselves Anonymous.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:49): at one point i was part of they're seemingly endless ranks, but i have indeed found the error in their ways and chosen my own path
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:49): TEXAS
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:49): Where is your unit?
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:51): RAMIREZ, TAKE POINT.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:51): I believe that, that information has been deemed confidential by my superiors...
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:52): NEGATIVE. RAMIERZ WE HAVE TANGO FOXTROT. ENGAGE.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:52): I AM RAMIREZ
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:53): RAMIREZ FIRE RPG!
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:53): and thus the plot twists
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:53): FIRING!
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:53): TANGO NEUTRALIZED
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:54): OH NO YOU DIDN'T.
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:54): Seriously. Add me on MSN. And for the record, unit resides at Whiskey Hotel.
f13ee31d453840def170d71fd96bf28d (10:54): I declined the last add.
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:55): ah yes
fba664425aeec4bd9ee81e22027683ad (10:55): thanks for the reminder
